# Hospital IT Commissioning Checklist

This checklist ensures IT readiness before hospital go-live.

## Infrastructure Readiness
- Data center / server room operational
- Network backbone tested (LAN/WAN)
- Redundant internet links configured
- Wi-Fi coverage validated in all clinical areas
- Power backup (UPS / DG) tested

## Core Systems
- HIS / HMIS configured and tested
- EMR workflows validated with clinicians
- LIS, PACS, RIS integrated and tested
- Billing and reporting verified

## End-User Readiness
- Workstations deployed and tested
- Printers, scanners, barcode devices configured
- User roles and access controls validated
- Login credentials issued

## Security & Compliance
- Access control policies implemented
- Audit logs enabled
- Data privacy controls in place
- Antivirus / endpoint security deployed
